            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2042192/">变态也有高下之分</a></h2>

                <div id="review_2042192_short" class="review-short" data-rid="2042192">
                    <div class="short-content">
                            <p class="spoiler-tip">这篇书评可能有关键情节透露</p>

